		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Interesting.</p>
<p>Problem with setting width is that you have to do it manually for every text that appears on buttons. And it doesn&#8217;t work all that great for me. It looks good on IE, but it cuts text off on FF1.0/Mac.</p>
